title: 339. Andy & DJ CTI: Biden's Climate Executive Orders, Antifa Vs. Bikers & Police Identify Victims In Indiana Mall Shooting
itunes:title: 339. Andy & DJ CTI: Biden's Climate Executive Orders, Antifa Vs. Bikers & Police Identify Victims In Indiana Mall Shooting
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss Biden's plan to issue an executive order for the climate crisis, Antifa being chased away after picking a fight with a biker gang, and the police identifying the victims along with the hero bystander who killed the shooter.
